  "bib_entries": {
    "39939646": {
      "title": "High-Energy Equivalence Theorem in Spontaneously Broken Supergravity",
      "abstract": "An equivalence theorem relating S-matrix elements with some external helicity \\ifmmode\\pm\\else\\textpm\\fi{}(1/2 gravitinos to S-matrix elements with corresponding external Goldstinos at high energy is rigorously proven from a set of Ward identities of N=1 supergravity. A more intuitive proof is given using the functional integral formalism. Similar equivalence theorems hold in general in theories possessing gauge properties spontaneously broken by a Higgs-type mechanism."
